{"id": "1494702495098867752", "channel_id": "1494670078489268324", "type": 0, "author_id": "204255221017214977", "author_name": "YAGPDB.xyz", "author_bot": true, "content": "Please be sure to check out our <#1304022827824844842>  section! Here are a few resources, tips, and walkthroughs to help you master the game:\r\n\r\n\r\n- [Morimens Compendium](<https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TCU7LJRzqKeuvLe97y_TfGZ-j6jq5bZX6hskAAJ2mFQ/edit?gid=167686509#gid=167686509>) by Mythag University\r\n- [Game Mechanics](https://discordapp.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1417994340177022981) by Mythag University\r\n- [Store Guide](https://discordapp.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1442292634575175710) by Mythag University\r\n- [Damage Formula](https://discordapp.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1384463374213189652) by Jynn             \r\n- [How To Aliemus 101 & 102](https://discordapp.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1387172781829128304) by Jynn  \r\n- [Morimens New Players Handbook](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1477730088299663431) by Cheri\r\n- [Boss Compendium](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1489244885025292328) by Mythag University\r\n- [Compilation of guide videos](<https://docs.google.com/document/d/1bnnR--yNl6r5cMljPoEF4bXC9HIoSK_WNUG7ucYGO6A/edit?usp=sharing>) by Kaly", "timestamp": "2026-04-17T14:14:05.061000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1494670078489268324", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "(Helpme!)Team building for Liz", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1494702926667579424", "channel_id": "1494670078489268324", "type": 19, "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "author_bot": false, "content": "liz is a sustained dps, she is about building up flames in your hand and then turning them into poison on the boss\n\nYou do this over and over until the boss has a bajillion poison and takes a bajillion damage every turn\n\nHer weakness is that she's a one trick pony, this is the only thing she can do. She has no defense and is poor against mob fights. She also has problems getting enough aliemus to exalt on her own\n\nA good team for liz is one that can shore up her weaknesses. Keep her alive, take care of trash mobs, feed her aliemus so she can do her thing", "timestamp": "2026-04-17T14:15:47.955000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["731859657202860143"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1494670078489268324", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1494670078489268324", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "(Helpme!)Team building for Liz", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1494703039595155526", "channel_id": "1494670078489268324", "type": 0, "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "author_bot": false, "content": "If you are new and have no characters, i recommend a caro/ultra team for liz", "timestamp": "2026-04-17T14:16:14.879000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1494670078489268324", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "(Helpme!)Team building for Liz", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1494703197506244691", "channel_id": "1494670078489268324", "type": 0, "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "author_bot": false, "content": "i have a new account where i mainly built liz and this team works well for story mode\n\nLeigh is used for long boss fights, aigis for short fights", "timestamp": "2026-04-17T14:16:52.528000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-17T14:17:41.930000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1494703196675772456", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-04-17_212957.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2499443, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494670078489268324/1494703196675772456/Screenshot_2026-04-17_212957.png?ex=69e39254&is=69e240d4&hm=d759e308b5e2c88b88a992df7ff8b8aa352d3bbc1db17735915343649fd76263&"}, {"id": "1494703197321822238", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-04-12_202318.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2518577, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494670078489268324/1494703197321822238/Screenshot_2026-04-12_202318.png?ex=69e39254&is=69e240d4&hm=bb5fe076dc0f11afb10e6ce93f4d0db3cefebef92af2f0fb710918114f25fd26&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1494670078489268324", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "(Helpme!)Team building for Liz", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
